--- /dev/null
+++ b/docs/api/structures/web-policy-handler-response.md
@@ -0,0 +1,9 @@
+# WebPolicyHandlerResponse Object
+
+* `action` string - The action to take for the policy check. Can be `default`,
+  `allow`, or `deny`.
+
+`default` preserves Chromium's normal policy behavior. `allow` allows this
+specific policy check to continue even when Chromium's policy would block it.
+`deny` blocks this specific policy check even when Chromium's policy would
+allow it.
